id n't take action for several months, the <PERSON> Cottams </PERSON> decided to retreat from the outside world, <PERSON> Flora </PERSON> said. They moved back to <LOCATION> Luzerne </LOCATION> <LOCATION> County </LOCATION>, teaching their children at home, and turning to God for help from financial problems when <PERSON> Cottam </PERSON> lost his job as a truck driver, <PERSON> Flora </PERSON> said.
