Ends</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS throughout to UPDATE with party leader urging loyalty
to Solidarity government, Mazowiecki quote, other details; no pickup</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOHN DANISZEWSKI</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WARSAW, Poland (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
